Design Media Sharing Social Networking System

This system will allow users to share post, photos and videos.
Get other user profile details
Send friend request

– Availability
– Reliability
– Resiliency
– Durability
– Cost Performance

API's
    /addPost
    /getPost
    /deletePost

Schema
    User - id, name, mobile, email
    UserFriends - id, userId, friendId
    Post - id, userId, postType, post, postPath